     - "access_switches": Access layer switches (id, status, location)
     - "links": Network links between devices (from, to, bandwidth_gbps, utilization_percent)
   - "device_metrics": Performance metrics for devices/interfaces (device, interface, metric, values with timestamps)
   - "log_snippets": Network device log entries (timestamp, level, device, message)
   - "related_incidents": Similar past incidents if any (id, date, location, resolution, similarity)

